{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"5":"Prayer (Kitab Al-Salat): Voluntary Prayers"},"section_detail":{"5":{"hadithnumber_first":1250,"hadithnumber_last":1370,"arabicnumber_first":1250,"arabicnumber_last":1370}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1318,"arabicnumber":1318,"text":"Rapporté par Aïcha رضي الله عنها : Quand il était avec moi, il dormait à l’aube. Par là, elle parlait du Prophète ﷺ","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (1133) Sahih Muslim (742)"}],"reference":{"book":5,"hadith":69}}]}